10 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 74 O.S. 2021, Section 85.5a, is
11 amended to read as follows:
12 Section 85.5a. A. Except for the state fleet card, the state
13 purchase card program administered by the Purchasing Division is the
14 only card program authorized for use by state agencies.
15 B. On a monthly basis the State Purchasing Director and
16 institutions of higher education shall provide to the Director of
17 the Office of Management and Enterprise Services (OMES) a complete
18 listing in electronic format of all transactions paid by a state
19 purchase card. The list shall contain the name of the purchaser and
20 purchasing agency, amount of purchase and all available descriptions
21 of items purchased.
22 C. Upon receipt of the list described in subsection B of this
23 section, the Director of the OMES shall allow the public access to
